{"title":"阿婆做的千家饭（小唱）","authors":["张永枚"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":12,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿婆做的千家饭（小唱）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李阿婆我刚满六十三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营长要我去敬老院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好说歹说我也不干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当上了食堂炊事员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘媳妇们去生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全排的饭菜我包干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看我还是围着锅台转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今我做的是千家饭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双手做出千家饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户都吃得欢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从我的食堂一开张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员的体重往上添！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逢一吃荤巧打算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又蒸又炖炒三鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再大的胃口也管你饱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我做的饭菜不要钱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民有了铁饭碗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人逢喜事我手不闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养猪喂鸡还要浇菜园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有个外号叫“不夜天”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李阿婆我刚满六十三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要搞共产正当年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你问我几时去敬老院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要再干一百年！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}